<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/froala-editor@latest/css/froala_editor.pkgd.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    type="text/css" />
  <title>
    <%= title %>
  </title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-9gVQ4dYFwwWSjIDZnLEWnxCjeSWFphJiwGPXr1jddIhOegiu1FwO5qRGvFXOdJZ4" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style5.css' />

  <script src="/javascripts/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
  <script defer src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.13/js/solid.js"
    integrity="sha384-tzzSw1/Vo+0N5UhStP3bvwWPq+uvzCMfrN1fEFe+xBmv1C/AtVX5K0uZtmcHitFZ" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </script>
  <script defer src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.13/js/fontawesome.js"
    integrity="sha384-6OIrr52G08NpOFSZdxxz1xdNSndlD4vdcf/q2myIUVO0VsqaGHJsB0RaBE01VTOY" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </script>
</head>

<body>
  <div>
    <%-header%>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <table align="center" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width='1000px'>
      <tr>
        <td rowspan="6" align "center"><img style="border: 1px solid#e9e9e9;" src="/<%=product.Pimage%>" width=500px
            height=400px /></td>
        <td width=300px align="left" style="color:darkgoldenrod">
          <h1 style="font-size: 30px"><%=product.Pname%></h1>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td align="left">
          <% if(product.Salerate == 0) { %>
          <h1><%=Number(product.Price).toLocaleString('en')%>원</h1>
          <% } %>
          <% if(product.Salerate != 0) { %>
          <div style="font-size: 40px; color: #e9e9e9;">
            <strike><%=Number(product.Price).toLocaleString('en')%>원</strike></div>
          <div style="font-size: 40px"><strong style="color: red;"><%=product.Salerate%>%</strong>
            <strong><%=Number(saleprice).toLocaleString('en')%>원</strong></div>
          <% } %>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <hr style="border-style:dotted">
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td align="left">
          <div style="font-size: 20px">원산지: 국내산</div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td align="left">
          <div style="font-size: 20px">출시일: <%=date%></div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td align="left" colspan=" 2"><button
            style="border-radius: 10px; font-size:20px; background-color: white; border-color: darkgoldenrod; font-size:10px; padding: 10px 10px;"
            onclick="window.location.href = '/customer/detail/<%=product.PID%>/buy'">구매하기</button>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td colspan="2">
          <hr>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td align="left" colspan=" 2">
          <strong style="font-size:20px;">상세 설명</strong>
          <p><%-product.Pdesc%>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <br><br>
      <tr>
        <td colspan="2">
          <hr>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td align="left" colspan=" 2">
          <strong style="font-size:20px;">교환 및 반품</strong>
          <p> - 식품 특성상 제품 하자를 제외한 개봉 후 반품 및 환불은 불가합니다.</p>
          <p> - 고객님의 단순 변심으로 인한 교환 및 반품은 어려우며, 발송 중 고객님의 부재로 인한 미수령 후 반송 시 반품은 불가합니다.</p>
          <p> - 제품에 문제가 있거나 주문한 상품과 동일하지 않은 상품을 받으신 경우 연락바랍니다.</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td align="left" colspan=" 2">
          <hr>
          <strong style="font-size:20px;">리뷰</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <%
      for(var i=0; i<reviews.length; i++)
      {
          var review = reviews[i];
      %>
      <tr>
        <td align="left">
          <hr>
          <br>
          <p><%=review.Rname%></p>
          <p><strong style="font-size:1px;"><%=review.Rtime%></strong></p>
          <% 
          for(var j = 0; j < review.Star; j++) { %>
          ★
          <% } %>
          <br>
          <p><%=review.Review%></p>
          <br>
          <hr>
        </td>
        <td>
          <img style="border: 1px solid#e9e9e9;" src="/<%=review.Rimage%>" width=150px height=150px />
        </td>
        <br>
      </tr>
      <%
      }
      %>
      <hr>
    </table>
    <button class="btn btn-primary"
      onclick="window.location.href = '/customer/detail/<%=product.PID%>/review'">작성</button>
  </div>

</body>

</html>